10  package de.funfried.netbeans.plugins.external.formatter.ui;
11  
12  import javax.swing.Icon;
13  
14  import org.netbeans.api.annotations.common.StaticResource;
15  import org.openide.util.ImageUtilities;
16  
17  /**
18   * Interface for holding application icons.
19   *
20   * @author bahlef
21   */
22  public interface Icons {
23  	/**
24  	 * Path to the external icon.
25  	 */
26  	@StaticResource
27  	public static final String EXTERNAL_FORMATTER_ICON_PATH = "de/funfried/netbeans/plugins/external/formatter/external.gif";
28  
29  	/**
30  	 * Path to the Eclipse icon.
31  	 */
32  	@StaticResource
33  	public static final String ECLIPSE_ICON_PATH = "de/funfried/netbeans/plugins/external/formatter/eclipse.gif";
34  
35  	/**
36  	 * Path to the Google icon.
37  	 */
38  	@StaticResource
39  	public static final String GOOGLE_ICON_PATH = "de/funfried/netbeans/plugins/external/formatter/google.gif";
40  
41  	/**
42  	 * Path to the NetBeans icon.
43  	 */
44  	@StaticResource
45  	public static final String NETBEANS_ICON_PATH = "de/funfried/netbeans/plugins/external/formatter/netbeans.gif";
46  
47  	/**
48  	 * External icon.
49  	 */
50  	public static final Icon ICON_EXTERNAL = ImageUtilities.image2Icon(ImageUtilities.loadImage(EXTERNAL_FORMATTER_ICON_PATH));
51  
52  	/**
53  	 * Eclipse icon.
54  	 */
55  	public static final Icon ICON_ECLIPSE = ImageUtilities.image2Icon(ImageUtilities.loadImage(ECLIPSE_ICON_PATH));
56  
57  	/**
58  	 * Google icon.
59  	 */
60  	public static final Icon ICON_GOOGLE = ImageUtilities.image2Icon(ImageUtilities.loadImage(GOOGLE_ICON_PATH));
61  
62  	/**
63  	 * NetBeans icon.
64  	 */
65  	public static final Icon ICON_NETBEANS = ImageUtilities.image2Icon(ImageUtilities.loadImage(NETBEANS_ICON_PATH));
66  }
